visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Glass Antiqua

designer: Denis Masharov

approved: true
description: <p>This is revival of the 1913 typeface \
  "Glass Antiqua" by "Genzsch &amp; Heyse" found in \
  the Taschen book "Type: A Visual History of \
  Typefaces and Graphic Styles, 1901-1938." \
  A magnificent and unique design with a Jugenstile \
  fleur, combining Slab Serif and Antiqua, plus \
  elements of cursive calligraphy. It is suitable \
  for any purpose, giving a text a retro feel and \
  soft informal look. The character set is extended \
  but the originals are carefully restored, and all \
  are patiently spaced and kerned.</p>

font.GlassAntiqua-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.GlassAntiqua-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

